description:
This is a 51 minute workout called 'Extreme Fat Burning Workout - 50 Minute Indoor Cycling Class' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Subscribe to GCN Training: https://gcn.eu/GCNTraining

Welcome to GCN's fat burning 50 minute indoor cycling workout.

GCN's 50 minute indoor cycling workout is designed as a fat burning workout. We think this could be one of our toughest sessions yet.

Session leader Jessica Palmer takes through a 50 minute class (including warm up and warm down) that targets pedalling technique with sustained hard efforts.

Feel the burn!

Want to try another of our sessions? Check out our playlist: http://gcn.eu/gcntraining

Thanks to Jessica: @ibike_bristol

And thanks to Nuffield Health Bristol!
